## Print Products — Coasters

### Glossed Cork Coaster

| Field | Value |
|---|---|
| Print area | 3.74″ × 3.74″ (square) |
| Construction | Cork back, MDF core, gloss top |
| Pixels at 300 DPI | 1,122 × 1,122 |
| Pixels at 200 DPI | 748 × 748 |

**Notes:** Fourthwall's coaster is cork-backed with gloss coating — not ceramic. Small physical size means almost any master canvas provides more than enough resolution. However, coasters are held close (12–18 inches), so they need the full 300 DPI. Crop detail-rich areas for coasters — they reward close-up interest.

