Framed High-Quality Matte Poster. 260 g/m² paper (heavier than unframed). 0.75″ Ayous wood frame. Acrylite front protector. Manufactured by Printful.

Pixel requirements are identical to unframed posters (same print area). Available in 12 sizes. OIS currently sells two:

### 10 × 10 inches (Framed)

| Field | Value |
|---|---|
| Print area | 10″ × 10″ |
| Frame | 0.75″ Ayous wood |
| Pixels at 300 DPI | 3,000 × 3,000 |

### 18 × 24 inches (Framed)

| Field | Value |
|---|---|
| Print area | 18″ × 24″ |
| Frame | 0.75″ Ayous wood |
| Pixels at 300 DPI | 5,400 × 7,200 |

**Notes:** Cannot ship to Australia (wood import regulations). The frame adds visual border, so the printed art can extend to the edge without concern about handling damage. Same export file works for both framed and unframed versions of the same size.

