## Digital Platform Assets

All digital assets should be exported as PNG in sRGB at exact platform dimensions. No bleed needed. Optimize for file size (use PNG-8 for simple graphics, PNG-24/32 for complex art with transparency).

### YouTube

| Asset | Dimensions | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| Banner (upload) | 2560 × 1440px | Full canvas for TV display |
| Banner safe zone | 1546 × 423px | Centered. All text/logos here. |
| Banner (desktop) | 2560 × 423px | Full width, cropped top/bottom |
| Profile picture | 800 × 800px | Displayed as circle |
| Thumbnail | 1280 × 720px | Max 2 MB |

**YouTube banner is the trickiest asset.** Upload the full 2560 × 1440 canvas, but design all critical content within the 1546 × 423 centered safe zone — the only area guaranteed visible on mobile, tablet, desktop, and TV. Everything outside the safe zone is background.

### Twitch

| Asset | Dimensions | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| Banner | 1200 × 480px | 1920 × 480 for retina |
| Profile picture | 800 × 800px | Min 256 × 256, circle crop |
| Offline screen | 1920 × 1080px | |

### Discord

| Asset | Dimensions | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| Server banner | 960 × 540px | Top ~28% overlapped by name |
| Server icon | 512 × 512px | Circle crop |

### Other Platforms

| Platform | Asset | Dimensions |
|---|---|---|
| Instagram | Profile pic | 320 × 320px (circle) |
| Instagram | Feed (square) | 1080 × 1080px |
| Instagram | Feed (portrait) | 1080 × 1350px (4:5) |
| Instagram | Stories/Reels | 1080 × 1920px (9:16) |
| TikTok | Profile pic | 1080 × 1080px (circle) |
| X/Twitter | Header | 1500 × 500px |
| X/Twitter | Profile pic | 400 × 400px (circle) |
| Facebook | Page cover | 851 × 315px |
| Facebook | Profile pic | 320 × 320px (circle) |

